{"tid":1127023,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"My 中學身涯","createTime":"2019-04-26T19:35:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-27T02:17:04.000Z","uid":250690,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"df372552bc459ee5c50ebf2c9181425a6baea23f","tid":1127023,"uid":250690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T19:35:45.000Z","msg":"我叫做夏語。<br />\n<br />\n我係學校有三個好朋友，<br />\n<br />\n一個叫詩琪，一個係心願，一個係晶燃。<br />\n<br />\n我係一個普普通通嘅中一女學生。<br />\n<br />\n而每個中學生涯點可以缺少一個暗戀對象呢。<br />\n<br />\n而我嘅暗戀對象就係同我同班嘅一個男仔。<br />\n<br />\n佢叫做夏宇，我地嗰名嘅啱啱好一樣讀音。<br />\n<br />\n有時會被人笑我地好襯。<br />\n<br />\n佢好受歡迎，因為佢讀書勁、運動好、音樂都超好、175cm高、最重要係佢好靚仔。<br />\n<br />\n我點解會鐘意佢，我都唔清楚...<br />\n<br />\n可能係一見鐘情或者係佢嘅性格吸引我?<br />\n<br />\n反正我凈係知道佢永遠都唔睇得上我呢嗰&ldquo;路人&rdquo;"},{"pid":"0954f4a20045db05323c994767cb210ba054a3c9","tid":1127023,"uid":29846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T19:52:59.000Z","msg":"我迷失在.* 這場_&times;&deg;愛情遊戲？"},{"pid":"4dc800ff20d7a9dde5cb4b220e4cc99cf32f40d8","tid":1127023,"uid":250690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0954f4a20045db05323c994767cb210ba054a3c9","tid":1127023,"uid":29846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T19:52:59.000Z","msg":"我迷失在.* 這場_&times;&deg;愛情遊戲？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T19:53:45.000Z","msg":"?"},{"pid":"b656b469d384ae8489578683461275cf21d32e86","tid":1127023,"uid":209391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T02:17:04.000Z","msg":"乜撚嘢叫身涯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}